# Repository Guide

Read and follow the root [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) before editing. It is the
canonical guide shared by Cursor, Codex, and Claude Code.

`app/mqtt_contract.py` owns the advertised schema. `app/broker.py` owns MQTT
transport, retained publications, RPC replay, and listener activity.
`app/main.py` owns API orchestration, commands, and follow-up refreshes.

Before finishing a Python change, run the focused tests plus:

```sh
.venv/bin/python -m pytest -q
.venv/bin/ruff check .
```

Keep credentials and tokens out of code, tests, logs, and commits. Do not send
live Spotify commands, alter OAuth state, deploy containers, or clear persisted
state unless the task explicitly requires that external action.
